    "It is calculated as: R-Precision = 𝑟𝑒𝑡 𝑞,𝑅 𝑟𝑒𝑙 𝑞,where 𝑟𝑒𝑡 𝑞,𝑅 is the number of relevant documents retrieved within the top 𝑅 positions, and 𝑅 is equivalent to 𝑟𝑒𝑙 𝑞.",
    "Mean Reciprocal Rank (MRR).",
    "MRR reflects the average rank position of the first relevant document returned in the search results.",
